    "body": "`getrawtransaction()` now accepts a wtxid in addition to a txid. If the initial txid lookup fails, the hash is retried as a wtxid against the mempool. Wtxid lookup is mempool-only since the txindex indexes by txid.\r\n\r\nCloses #34013\r\n",
